World Liar Contest. Khrushchev takes the stage: - The current generation of Soviet people will live under communism! They applauded him. Bush comes out: - We found biological weapons in Iraq! They also patted him. Biden comes out. I didn't have time to open my mouth - a storm of applause from the whole hall. Judge: You don't have to say anything. Second place. - Why not the first? - Yes, here one said that there are no oligarchs in Russia.